Package: Waypoint
Type: Package
Title: Conversion, Validation, Formatting and Printing of Geographic Coordinates
Version: 1.0.0.00022
Date: 2025-03-06
Author: Mark Eisler
Maintainer: Mark Eisler <mark@markeisler.com>
Description: The Waypoint R package enables conversion, validation, and neat formatting and printing of individual geographic positional coordinates and waypoints of paired latitude and longitude. Coordinates and waypoints may be converted easily and rapidly between (i) decimal degree, (ii) degrees and minutes, and (iii) degrees, minutes and seconds formats.
